{"tid":509973,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［好奇害死貓系列］有時啲野真係唔知好過知","createTime":"2017-12-26T03:26:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T04:03:29.000Z","uid":103320,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ba448c2681a290015214ef81cf8e6ae8a1b86983","tid":509973,"uid":103320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T03:26:44.000Z","msg":"同另一半識左兩年，前排一齊左<br />\n其實一開頭識佢已經對佢有啲好感<br />\n而且識落都幾純，唔會濫<br />\n好啦講番正題，近排同佢一齊左<br />\n有日佢漏左手機係我到<br />\n我見到佢ig啲direct message係咁彈出黎<br />\n我衰 手多 走去開黎睇<br />\n見到佢其實同好多異性有聯絡<br />\n見到佢成日主覆人ig story<br />\n又有啲係曖昧既對話 （但係幾個月前 個時未同佢一齊）<br />\n但有一個message睇完真係好撚sad<br />\n睇到佢同我一齊前個嗰月 佢仲掛住緊ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇完個下 我心都沉埋<br />\n我而家 真係有啲唔識點對住佢"},{"pid":"3347dce5af4a3ba830827d873a6fef5a9041039c","tid":509973,"uid":157579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T03:43:08.000Z","msg":"下次唔好喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee5e8732369ea1ef421e986f6877c9107a7f165e","tid":509973,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T03:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af44a0a705509ed7ffddac26379598f1d2ca91c","tid":509973,"uid":103320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T03:51:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3abd08cc26fe41ff91ab926af9223435e4f0ab49","tid":509973,"uid":156547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T04:03:29.000Z","msg":"扑左未？"}]}